casebody.data:
No. 09-930. Kenyon B. Fitzgerald, Jr., et al., Petitioners v. Wade F. B. Thompson, et al. 561 U.S. 1038, 130 S. Ct. 3500,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1114,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5306. June 28, 2010.

Motion of American Legion, Department of New York for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae out of time denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.

Same case below, 353 Fed. Appx. 532.
